{"tid":637931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人就係on9 同慘","createTime":"2018-04-22T09:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T09:37:41.000Z","uid":132030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddad587d553fdd8779dad75baedad31364229f2c","tid":637931,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"去完日本之後 就知道求其一間拉麵店都好平<br />\n基本上係希望窮人都食到 <br />\n但香港食拉麵竟然係有錢人食 要用成百蚊咁去買一碗人地窮人都食到嘅野 仲要排撚曬隊去食<br />\n啲人set 到個麵咁撚貴 有啲係因為租貴 有啲係因為當香港人水魚<br />\n所以去過日本之後 我一定減少係香港食拉麵"},{"pid":"dad5254a45b4cefa8023c1d864af2f909c63c772","tid":637931,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"香港就係咁可悲"},{"pid":"39a483aca577b96e785dfeb7b0db6cd17ca9bcd6","tid":637931,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a434912795c60093f589ab965e12f59c2926f22","tid":637931,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b16b9ae2e56a1161632238ed154150fde94103a6","tid":637931,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ed59067d06f8ece16c227fc5b8ed4d083a22839","tid":637931,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:30:25.000Z","msg":"正經野無人討論"},{"pid":"a4cecc8de66f7787f445a2d4b4609d22e24ace8c","tid":637931,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"old news<br />\n<br />\n不過我慶少少ge<br />\n有d撚樣會同我講<br />\n「去遠d行下」<br />\n「食好d」<br />\n<br />\n你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出到老閪遠少少,食茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好食我都算<br />\n多d見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心諗香港地有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/n